node.title: Body of 11-year-old girl recovered from ManawatÅ« River
node.description: The search for a 25-year-old remains ongoing.
node.content: ["A search and rescue team scouring the Manawat\u016b River have recovered the body of one of two people who disappeared in the Manawat\u016b River on December 29.", "While formal identification is yet to take place, police said in a press release they believe it to be the body of the 11-year-old girl.", "Police extends its condolences to the girl's family and loved ones.", "A search for the 25-year-old woman who is still missing will continue today.", "The 11-year-old girl got into trouble swimming on Wednesday and a 25-year-old woman went in after her, but both failed to resurface.", "The crews spent that evening looking for any sign of the missing pair in the murky, swollen waters of the river as their families watched from the shore.", "\"It is really, really sad. They cannot believe this is real,\" family spokesperson Eh Doh Soe told Newshub.", "The missing woman had a one-year-old baby, he said."]
